0.1, respectively. The complex absorption-line properties of Mrk\n231, an ultraluminous infrared galaxy which is optically classified as a\nSeyfert 1, are discussed separately in an appendix.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jan 2002 17:34:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
