 also show that the depression of continuum flux strongly\nsuppresses the equivalent width of the ion cyclotron line and therefore makes\nthe line more difficult to observe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jan 2002 23:23:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2002 19:11:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2002 18:20:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
